Package eu.profinit.manta.connector.erstudio.model

Interface CompositeDataObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataObject, Layered, Mappable<CompositeDataObject>, eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.generator.modeling.common.nodes.NodeMetadata
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeDataObjectImpl
    public interface CompositeDataObject
extends DataObject, Mappable<CompositeDataObject>
    Depending on its AbstractionLayer this is a contract of a TableAbstractionLayer.PHYSICAL or of an EntityAbstractionLayer.LOGICAL. The object implementing this interface is a parent of SimpleDataObject objects that are modeled on the same AbstractionLayer. Every SimpleDataObject contained in CompositeDataObject must have a unique name.
